Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.61,0:01:56.19,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想要沉溺其中吧  妄想無論何時都如水之味
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.19,0:01:57.69,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}outside  noside
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.69,0:02:02.19,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}若是還不夠的話  就把一切都展現出來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.19,0:02:05.20,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}來吧  naked  dive  將感情釋放
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.20,0:02:08.18,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}去確定屬於你的真實
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.18,0:02:11.25,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對了  naked  dive  不斷追尋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.25,0:02:14.37,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}屬於自己內心的那份衝動不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.37,0:02:17.54,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}making  your  world  盡情地呼喊吧
